			<p>CryoLand provides a fully validated and standardized Snow, Glacier and Lake / River Ice service within the Global Monitoring of Environment and Security (GMES / Copernicus) framework of the European Commission. The products and services have been specified and consolidated by users from different fields of application, organized in the CryoLand User Group.</p>
