						<li> «<u>daily_SSW_SouthNorway_Optical</u>»:<br>Demonstration product based on temporal observations of snow temperature and snow grain size. Samples for south Norway periodically provided daily for the snowmelt season. Available for full snow cover only. Partial snow cover indicated and clouds masked. Spatial resolution 0.01° x 0.01°.</li>
