				<h4>Integration into GIS</h4>
				<p>Unfortunately, so far we are not aware on any implementation which allow accessing an OGC WCS interface from within a GIS application.</p>
				<p>
				</p><ul>
					<li>How-To access the CryoLand OGC-WMS interface from within QGIS<br>
					The Document <a href="http://cryoland.enveo.at/downloads/CryoLand4Newbies/CryoLand4Newbies.pdf">CryoLand4Newbies</a> provides a short overview about the products and functionalities provided by the CryoLand GeoPortal. There you'll also find a comprehensive guide on how-to access the CryoLand OGC-WMS interface from within QGIS.<br>
					</li>
